      <title>参议院多数党领袖将遗产税废除在共和党法案会谈中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/thune-pitches-estate-tax-repeal-as-gop-advances-bill-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院多数党领袖约翰·杜恩（John Thune）认可了对遗产税的全面废除，并确定了对一些最富有的美国人的命运的征收，因为共和党人选拔了大量的经济方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/thune-pitches-estate-tax-repeal-as-gop-advances-bill-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 16:38:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普官员要求最高法院停止教师赠款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-administration-asks-supreme-court-to-halt-teacher-grants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府要求美国最高法院许可，以扣留可能数亿美元的教师培训赠款，并再次寻求高等法院的紧急帮助，以削减已建立的联邦支出计划的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-administration-asks-supreme-court-to-halt-teacher-grants</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 16:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普今天下午宣布自动关税，白宫说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-prepares-auto-tariff-announcement-as-soon-as-wednesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据白宫称，唐纳德·特朗普总统将于周三宣布对汽车行业的关税，此举将在下周在更广泛的关税推动下与全球贸易伙伴的战斗升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-prepares-auto-tariff-announcement-as-soon-as-wednesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 15:56:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bolsonaro要接受政变的审判，巴西的顶级法院小组规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/bolsonaro-to-stand-trial-on-coup-charges-top-court-panel-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西前总统杰尔·博尔森罗（Jair Bolsonaro）将在最高法院一致投票接受对他的刑事指控之后，将对他2022年大选后企图进行政变进行审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/bolsonaro-to-stand-trial-on-coup-charges-top-court-panel-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 15:29:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gabbard承认敏感攻击计划已在聊天中分享</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/gabbard-says-no-classified-info-shared-as-chat-texts-published</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家情报局局长塔尔西·加巴德（Tulsi Gabbard）周三承认，在美国官员之间的一次聊天中，计划对也门的胡塞部队进行袭击的细节，这些官员无意间将包括新闻工作者包括在内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/gabbard-says-no-classified-info-shared-as-chat-texts-published</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 14:51:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>邦迪将委内瑞拉驱逐出境归咎于法官的“矛盾”命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/bondi-blames-deportation-fight-on-judge-s-contradictory-orders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总检察长帕姆·邦迪（Pam Bondi）否认，政府违反了一名联邦法官的命令，反对被指控的委内瑞拉帮派成员驱逐出境，而不是责怪他的“矛盾”口头和书面裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/bondi-blames-deportation-fight-on-judge-s-contradictory-orders</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 13:37:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>释放信号成绩单菌株特朗普出价抗拒抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/atlantic-releases-details-of-signal-text-chain-on-houthi-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统和顶级盟友（Top Allies）努力抵制对新闻记者无意中批评的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/atlantic-releases-details-of-signal-text-chain-on-houthi-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 13:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
